; Coverage test for xact.cc
; Tests auto-xact cost derivation with per-unit price (@).
; When the initial post uses per-unit price notation, the auto-generated
; amount derives its cost by multiplying price * amount.
; This exercises the per-unit branch (not ANNOTATION_PRICE_NOT_PER_UNIT).

= Expenses:Energy
    Liabilities:Tax  (amount)
    Assets:Tax       (-amount)

2024/03/01 Electric Bill
    Expenses:Energy       100 kWh @ 0.72 EUR
    Assets:Checking

test reg --generated
24-Mar-01 Electric Bill         Expenses:Energy             100 kWh      100 kWh
                                Assets:Checking              EUR-72       EUR-72
                                                                         100 kWh
                                Liabilities:Tax             100 kWh       EUR-72
                                                                         200 kWh
                                Assets:Tax                 -100 kWh       EUR-72
                                                                         100 kWh
end test
